FT  01 NOV 94 / Dental patients warned of queues
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Dental patients were warned yesterday that they will have to queue for
health service treatment under a planned shake-up.
The British Dental Association, in its response to a green paper published
last July, added that patients would have to pay more for treatment.
