FT  29 OCT 94 / FT SCORE CONVERSION TABLE
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
FT SCORE CONVERSION TABLE
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
FT score         Typical grades
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
   1.65                AAA
   1.4                 BBB
   1.18                BCC
   1.08                CCC
   0.86                CDD
   0.6                 DDE
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Assumes average pupil took three A-levels.
Grades are higher if average pupil took less than three A-levels - a 1.0
score could represent BB, not CCC. All figures approximate.
